SUBSTITUTE FOR
HOUSE BILL NO. 4728
A bill to amend 1980 PA 299, entitled
"Occupational code,"
by amending section 303a (MCL 339.303a), as amended by 2014 PA 265,
and by adding article 14A.
THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF MICHIGAN ENACT:
1 Sec. 303a. The term of office of a member of a board appointed
2 under this article shall commence commences on 1 of the following
3 dates, as applicable:
4 Accountancy July 1
5 Architects April 1
6 Barbers October 1
7 Collection agencies July 1
