7 (8) An individual who knowingly provides false information
8 regarding the individual's identity, criminal convictions, or
9 substantiated findings on a statement described in subsection
10 (5)(b) is guilty of a misdemeanor punishable by imprisonment for
11 not more than 93 days or a fine of not more than $500.00, or both.
